{"tid":2017357,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間記者會批監警會反修例審視報告淡化警暴","createTime":"2020-05-15T05:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T07:36:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2e0f287d3fd47a5e104befab198706cef6500d","tid":2017357,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"民間記者會批監警會反修例審視報告淡化警暴<br />\n15.05.2020 11:44<br />\n<br />\n監警會下午將發表反修例運動的審視報告，監警會主席梁定邦早前指，報告將涵蓋公眾關注的多場示威衝突，但不會評論警隊高層或個別警員有否行為失當，只會陳述監警會收到的投訴內容。民間記者會發言人指，報告未有就721及831事件中，被指有警黑勾結、血腥鎮壓等情況作出合理解釋，批評報告淡化警暴，企圖為政權及警隊的失誤遮醜。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，監警會並無法定調查權，毫無公信力，亦非大眾要求的獨立調查委員會，又認為委員會必須調查，政府推行《逃犯條例》背後的詳細決策、警隊制度腐化等問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287645&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1287645%26csid%3D261_341&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRerkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=04577b13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287645&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f134984623ec05ce54f1e032604c60696a066b76","tid":2017357,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11a7fed54e8f9a616467c09f8a2618c16efe507","tid":2017357,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1362c9adce6e17f14deac1e50bdf999e37abff7e","tid":2017357,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco